The paper focuses on the interaction between humans and computers, specifically in solving image-based CAPTCHAs. This falls under the category of Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC). Additionally, the paper uses association rule mining to analyze the data collected from the experiment, which falls under the categories of Cybersecurity (cs.CY), Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI).
